<p>It comes after Katy put her own hilarious spin on MTV's first virtual Video Music Award ceremony on Sunday.</p>

<p>Posting to Instagram, the pop star only had on a nude breast pumping harness and a pair of grey high-waisted underwear as she posed in her bathroom mirror, five days after giving birth.    </p>

<p>'Hair and makeup by: <?php echo e('@'); ?>exhaustion,' captioned Perry jokingly, while also tagging the makers of her harness and underwear. </p>

<p>The Teenage Dream singer's hair was styled into a messy low ponytail as she prepared to pump for her newborn daughter Daisy Dove,</p>

<p>Making the best of it: It comes after Katy put her own hilarious spin on MTV's first virtual Video Music Award ceremony on Sunday</p>

<p>Katy's skin looked enviably clear and the tired singer stood with one arm out to her side as she confidently displayed her post-baby body. </p>

<p>Perry has a lengthy history and obvious love for the VMAs, being that she hosted the annual award show in 2017.</p>

<p>The Grammy Award nominee shares her first child with fiancé Orlando, 43. Bloom also has a nine-year-old son Flynn with ex Miranda Kerr, 37.</p>

